## API Endpoints

### Authentication
- `POST /api/auth/register` - Register new user
- `POST /api/auth/login` - User login
- `POST /api/auth/logout` - User logout
- `POST /api/auth/verify` - Verify token
- `POST /api/auth/refresh` - Refresh token

### Chat
- `POST /api/chat/message` - Send message
- `GET /api/chat/history` - Get chat history
- `GET /api/chat/:chatId` - Get specific chat
- `DELETE /api/chat/:chatId` - Delete chat
- `POST /api/chat/create` - Create new chat
- `POST /api/chat/predict` - Get AI prediction

### Users
- `GET /api/users/profile` - Get user profile
- `PUT /api/users/profile` - Update profile
- `GET /api/users` - Get all users (Admin only)

## Environment Variables

### Client (.env)
```
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
VITE_APP_NAME=Concept Clarity
```

### Server (.env)
```
MONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/concept-clarity
JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret_key_change_this_in_production
PORT=5000
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key
PYTHON_SERVICE_URL=http://localhost:8000
NODE_ENV=development
```

### AI Service
No environment variables required for basic setup

## Architecture Highlights

### Clean Code Principles
- Separation of concerns (Controllers, Services, Models)
- Modular component structure
- Reusable services and utilities
- Environment-based configuration

### Security
- JWT token-based authentication
- Password hashing with bcryptjs
- Role-based middleware
- CORS protection
- Environment variable management

### Scalability
- Microservice architecture (AI service separate)
- MongoDB for scalable data storage
- Service abstraction (GPT fallback mechanism)
- Stateless API design

### User Experience
- Dark/Light theme support
- Responsive design
- Real-time chat interface
- Fast Vite build tool
- Tailwind CSS utilities

## Development Workflow

1. **Frontend Development**: Edit React components in `client/src`
2. **Backend Development**: Edit Node.js code in `server/`
3. **AI Development**: Update Python code in `ai-service/`
4. **Testing**: Each service can be tested independently

## Production Deployment

### Build Frontend
```bash
cd client
npm run build
```

### Build Backend
Ready to deploy as-is, ensure MongoDB connection string is updated

### Deploy AI Service
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
gunicorn -w 4 -k uvicorn.workers.UvicornWorker app:app
```

